The paper deals with a clustering problem in high-dimensional space, which is a common topic in computational geometry (cs.CG) and data structures (cs.DS). The problem also involves optimization and approximation algorithms, which are relevant to discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and machine learning (cs.LG).
